{{Infobox person | name = Dawn Stern | image = | imagesize = | alt = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{birth year and age|1966}}<!-- {{Birth date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | birth_place = [[Military base]] near [[Tokyo]], [[Japan]] | death_date = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} Death date then birth --> | death_place = | othername = | occupation = [[Actress]] and [[model (person)|model]] | years_active = Since 1996 | spouse = [[Stephan Wolfert]] | domesticpartner = | website = }} '''Dawn Stern''' (born 1966) is an [[United States|American]] [[film]] and [[television]] [[actress]]; she is also a [[model (person)|model]].
==Early life and education== She was born on a [[military base]] near Tokyo, but was raised in [[O'Fallon, Illinois]], where she attended EK and [[O'Fallon Township High School]].
==Career== Stern has done both [[Runway (fashion)|runway]] and print modeling. In 1996 she moved to [[Los Angeles]], [[California]], and within six months was appearing as Allie Farrow on ''[[Viper (TV series)|Viper]]'', a [[science fiction|science-fiction]] [[television program|television series]] on the [[UPN]] [[Terrestrial television|broadcast]]-[[television network]]. From 2003 to 2004, she had a recurring role as Vanessa Lerner on the [[soap opera]] television series ''[[The Young and the Restless]]''.
She has appeared in over thirty television and two film productions.
==Personal life== She is married to [[Stephan Wolfert]], an actor and director.
